tags: spider man: into the spider verse
summary:
funniest things in spider-man: into the spider-verse according to me:
“i’m tired”
“are you mad at me? i feel like you’re mad at...
body:
funniest things in spider-man: into the spider-verse according to me:

  • “i’m tired”
  • “are you mad at me? i feel like you’re mad at me”
  • “i should go up there and help him. who am i kidding? i should NOT do that.”
  • “yeah, i think it’s a banksy”
  • the whole peter b. parker monologue when he is first introduced
  • peter b. parkers crying in the shower
  • when they’re trying to get away from the cemetery and they’re just… stuck… the whole time…
  • HOMELESS CORPSE
  • “pretty sure you just called me fat”
  • “did you break this?” “no, it… broke…”
  • “you have money, right?”
  • his sweatpants and the cape
  • the bagel-step is such a mood
  • the whole posture of wilson fisk aka kingpin makes me scream IT ISN’T RIGHT IN EVERY WAY
  • how does fisk fit through the door what?
  • “i am in the moment, it’s a terrible moment”
  • HIM SINGING SUNFLOWER (it’s been my jam since it came out)
  • “glitching? no!” *starts glitching*
  • he just keeps saying everything’ll be ok when clearly it’s all not ok
  • peter b. parker saying miles has to swing but he hasn’t taught miles how to yet so the whole “swinging”-scene
  • “you save it for comic-con”
  • “where’s that wind coming from? we’re in a basement”
  • john mulaney as peter porker
  • “he can do so much more. what else can you do?” “just those two things.” “jUST those two things!”
  • “do animals talk in this dimension? cuz i don’t wanna freak him out” *the boy passes out*
  • “what a pig” “i’m… right… here…”
  • LITERALLY HOW DOES FISK FIT? IT DOES NOT MAKE SENSE BITCH
  • “do i want kids?” (this is for real a really cute part)
  • “aww, did that feel like a cartoon?” *blows raspberry*
  • “we taught him that, right?” “i didn’t teach him that. and you definitely didn’t.”
  • how fisk is just hanging there

oh wow this is a big-ass list, idgaf though

ok i absolutely absolutely absolutely LOVE this movie, i am for real

i have not seen such a good movie for a long time and i have seen a lot of movies that have won awards this awards season

body:
Uuuugh….

When I see someone posting about SpiderFlash : 😀😀😃 reblog!!!! Like!!!!


When I realized they are starker : 🙃 let’s delete that reblog then…


I must insist : I will never call myself an anti. But I do have issues with that ship so I try not to interact with people shipping it.

I do not condone the death threat and unlimited hate I saw some people send to Starker shippers however.


So if you are an Antis OR a Starker Shipper, please don’t interact with me :) I’m really not confortable about that ship and I really can’t stand people sending death threats to others, so I can’t really interact with both here lmao…

I’m a total anti-anti.

And I am uncomfortable with the TonyxPeter ship.

So please :

If you are an anti : don’t interact.

If you ship Tony and Peter in a sexual way : don’t interact.
